set-up/install react:
  ->npm installl -g create-react-app

to check the version of react:-
  -> create-react-app --version / -v

to create reactjs Application
  -> create-react-app [application name]
      eg) create-react-app myapp

then automatically comes two commands as give below:-
  1) cd app_name                 application_name is when your are create the application on that time youare set the application name on line number  7. 
  2) npm start this command is used to start our application, after that click allow and set chrome